Configurar a interface de geranciamento.

int management 1/1
nameif MGMT
ip add 172.16.20.1 255.255.255.0
no sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Configurar o acesso SSH

ssh 172.16.20.0 255.255.255.0 MGMT

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Configurar username para acesso SSH

username admin password cisco privilege 15
aaa authentication ssh console LOCAL
